      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next big adventure with you! It runs beautifully and is perfect if you're looking for something dependable and clean without that brand-new price tag. Drop me a message if you\u2019d like to come see it!",
