    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E36 M3 is powered by the S52 3.2L inline-six, featuring a single-VANOS system that ensures a broad torque curve and immediate transient response. The drivetrain is anchored by a ZF 5-speed manual gearbox and a 3.23:1 limited-slip differential, providing superior mechanical grip. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul with an aluminum radiator and a reinforced water pump. The suspension geometry is well-preserved, maintaining the factory-intended balance and steering feedback. While the aesthetic shows character from spirited use, the longitudinal rigidity and powertrain health are exceptional for a driver-focused example.",
      "price": 36500.0,
