    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really great shape! It runs smoothly, looks wonderful, and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you need a dependable daily driver or something for those fun weekend road trips, this beauty is ready to roll. I\u2019ve truly loved driving it, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
