    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit. This naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, peaking at a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring refreshed bushings and dampers for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains robust and highly responsive. A purist-spec machine optimized for the enthusiast who values mechanical integrity over concours perfection.",
